{"tid":1262594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解今日好似冇人講警察拒絕出示委任證？","createTime":"2019-06-27T18:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T05:27:19.000Z","uid":68732,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6149fbabd33e6bcbd9227219dcbcc2820393d233","tid":1262594,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:18:02.000Z","msg":"呢條友今朝比佢d &quot;伙記&quot; 掩護下<br />\n一直拒絕出示委任證喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wgam4R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wgam4R.png&h=542a4502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n番到屋企忍唔住搵番立場姐姐條片<br />\n片都有埋： （23:19開始睇）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2277059785849928/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2277059785849928%2F&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=370ee2fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2277059785849928/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有之前添馬公園班疑似偽警員<br />\n陳警司又話：如果你要問既（委任證），我地就會比你<br />\n證據片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HXnrUjKYWAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHXnrUjKYWAE&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=d583cb29\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HXnrUjKYWAE</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我一直覺得警員如果可以唔依法例<br />\n自己選擇出唔出示委任證<br />\n絕對都係濫權既一種<br />\n亦都令市民更加不安 點解警權可以大過法律？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">致文宣巴絲</span></strong><br />\n雖然知你地好辛苦<br />\n但係呢種濫權方式絕對成為我地一粒好強力既子彈<br />\n有乜理由監警會叫我地要求警員比number同名＞先可以投訴<br />\n結果警員一直拒絕並搏慒，唔出示委任證<br />\n咁請問我地點樣投訴？<br />\n呢班知法犯法既警員絕對有理由懷疑就係個班脾氣暴燥，使用過份武力既濫權警喎？"},{"pid":"c0c5387bef969364ff93a19479ff5fc88833c2a8","tid":1262594,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6149a2788ca8dddfb0997d2f5431422e914474d9","tid":1262594,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"